src:
Live Streaming Shopee Liga 1 di Vidio: Persipura vs Bhayangkara
07 Nov 2019, 13:30 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Persipura Jayapura akan menjamu Bhayangkara FC pada pekan ke-27 Shopee Liga 1 2019, Kamis (7/11/2019). Pertandingan di Stadion Gelora Delta Sidoarjo ini bisa dinikmati melalui live streaming di Vidio.
Persipura saat ini menempati peringkat 3 dengan perolehan 43 poin dari 24 pertandingan (M12 S7 K5). Sementara itu, Bhayangkara berada di posisi 10 dengan 32 poin dari 26 laga (M7 S11 K8).
"Pada putaran pertama, tim lain berpikir mudah mengalahkan kami karena prestasi saat itu sedang buruk. Sekarang, kontestan lain berambisi mengalahkan kami dengan misi menahan laju Persipura di papan atas. Itulah menariknya sebuah kompetisi," kata pelatih Persipura, Jacksen F Tiago.
Jadwal lengkap dan live streaming pertandingan Persipura Jayapura vs Bhayangkara FC bisa Bolaneters simak di bawah ini.
text:
Live Streaming Shopee Liga 1 in Video: Persipura vs Bhayangkara
Nov 7 2019, 13:30 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Jayapura Persipura will host Bhayangkara FC in the 27th week of Shopee Liga 1 2019, Thursday (11/07/2019). The match at the Gelora Delta Sidoarjo Stadium can be enjoyed through live streaming at Vidio.
Roma are currently ranked 3 with 43 points from 24 matches (M12 S7 K5). Meanwhile, Bhayangkara is in 10th place with 32 points from 26 matches (M7 S11 K8).
"In the first round, the other team thought it was easy to beat us because the performance at that time was bad. Now, other contestants have ambitions to beat us with the mission of holding Persipura up at the top. That is the pull of a competition," said Persipura coach Jacksen F Tiago.
The full schedule and live streaming of Persipura Jayapura vs Bhayangkara FC matches can be seen below.
